The author of this package is Tom Andrews <tandrews@cse.unr.edu>

The author is indebted to Marco Maggi, who pioneered the idea of BASH
libraries, and provided the inspiration for this one. Marco's BASH
function library (mbfl) can currently be downloaded from:
<https://gna.org/projects/mbfl>

Please send bug reports for the lib_MTA package to:

<tandrews@cse.unr.edu>.

Questions on use of the library should be sent to:

libmta-support@lists.sourceforge.net

All email will be responded to as promptly as possible.
